snippet.description:

https://www.change.org/p/walt-disney-we-want-johnny-depp-back-as-captain-jack-sparrow

Piano and violin cover improvisation inspired by Gellert Grindelwald's theme / "The Thestral Chase" / "Relieve Him of His Wand" from Fantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald by James Newton Howard. Extended Version. Includes Hedwig's theme by John Williams.
